  <body>
   <p>If the Jews would be gathered again in Palestine or elsewhere, their Israelitish and messianic mission (Vide Isaiah, Ch. 46-6) would at once cease and that can not be, as long as there are nations and races to be freed and enlightened and linked to the golden or adamantine chain of the universal fraternity of all mankind.</p>
